The paper discusses the management of security credentials for distributed scientific computing, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and distributed computing (cs.DC). The paper also discusses the implementation of the SciTokens model, which involves software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL). Finally, the paper discusses the use of the Open Science Grid, which is a distributed computing infrastructure, further supporting the likelihood of the cs.Distributed category.
